title: 295: Broads Send in Their Dating Profiles!

description:
The #broadsquad is the BEST and these members of the squad have sent in their dating profiles (Tinder, Hinge, etc) for Bekah and Jess to analyze! But first Jess asks Bekah’s take on a disagreement that her and Evan got into right before the episode recording (00:00:00 - 00:24:00). Then they dive into broad’s dating profiles (starting 24 minutes in)! Pro Tip: this is a more visual episode as we go over the profile pictures so if you want to watch along - check out our youtube channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzx2N1qxFObhvSvf9tp7ayQ

A huge thank you to ALL the broads who sent in their profiles!
